Delta Sigma Simulator

Installation:
   Install Python 3.6

   Required libraries:
      numpy
      scipy
      matplotlib
      pandas
      pyqt5

   Install libraries with 1 or 2:
      1. pip install numpy, scipy, matplotlib, pyqt5
      2*. conda install numpy, scipy, matplotlib, pyqt5

      * 2 Preferred method. Requires installing miniconda from this website:
         https://conda.io/miniconda.html

Run GUI:
   Command line: Navigate to folder and type the following command:
      ./main.py

   IDE:
      open main.py and select run

CLI Usage:
      usage: deltasigma.py [-h] [-f FREQ] [-a AMPL] [-w WAVE] [-s SAMP] [-d DC]
                           [-n NOISE] [-sr SR] [-o OSR] [-v VREF] [-p PER]
                           [-or ORDER]
      
      optional arguments:
        -h, --help            show this help message and exit
        -f FREQ, --freq FREQ  Input frequency
        -a AMPL, --ampl AMPL  Input amplitude
        -w WAVE, --wave WAVE  Input waveform
        -s SAMP, --samp SAMP  Input samples
        -d DC, --dc DC        DC offset
        -n NOISE, --noise NOISE
                              Add noise
        -sr SR, --sr SR       Sampling rate
        -o OSR, --osr OSR     Oversampling multiplier
        -v VREF, --vref VREF  Reference voltage
        -p PER, --per PER     Number of periods
        -or ORDER, --order ORDER
                              First or Second order

Program:
   1. Enter desired values in appropriate fields.
   2. Click the green 'Run' button
